qy prmwqmw dy nwm-rs ivc msq rihMdw hY auh mnu`K (pRBU dI hzUrI ivc) kbUl huMdw hY ]7]
hy Twkur! mYN (gurU dI ikrpw nwl) eyDr EDr (hr QW) qYnUM hI (ivAwpk) vyKdw hW qy Awqmk Afolqw ivc itk ky qYnUM ismrdw hW,
